        "value": "Sakura-han's pre-abolition holdings by province (國) and district (郡), printed as a warichu note below the ○佐倉藩 marker (three stacked two-column bands; read each band right then left): Shimōsa 6 districts, Hitachi 2, Shimotsuke 2, Musashi 3, Sagami 3, Uzen 1 — 6 provinces, 17 districts total. The Hotta domain's territory was scattered across the Kantō plain plus an outlier in Dewa (Uzen)."
